{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_53_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 特大バースデーグミ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――四月三日　昼",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "うう……やっぱりさくらに渡すのはやめておいた方が\nいいかしら。でも私だったら凄く嬉しいものだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6000000477,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5718.2134892,
          "startTime": 12.3182135369
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、お疲れ様！\n私がどうかしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3633.3333332999996,
          "startTime": 18.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.3333351,
          "startTime": 24.0000000018
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら！？　いえ、その、ええと……\nた、誕生日おめでとう！　これ、プレゼント！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7400.000000000002,
          "startTime": 29.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "わあ、ありがとう！　これは……ホールケーキだ！\nあ、違う！　これ、ケーキじゃなくて……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "つ、作ってみたの……特大バースデーグミ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0666671594,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "と、特大バースデーグミ……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2333338261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "贈るなら一番美味しいお菓子にしようと思って\nそれで作ってみたんだけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "出来上がったこのグミを見たサニピのメンバーに\n「奇抜過ぎる」とか、いろいろコメントをもらって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3737176682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに私の趣味に偏り過ぎてるなって反省はしてるの\nだから、無理に受け取ってくれなくても――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ、くれないの！？\nすっごく素敵なプレゼントなのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　本当に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8333300114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　最高のプレゼントだよ！\n瑠依ちゃんにしか作れない唯一無二の作品だもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "本当に凄いよこれ！　ホールケーキ型の巨大グミ！\n色とりどりでマーブル模様のサイケデリックな見た目！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "さっそくいただいてみます！　がぶっと！\nおお、なんだかゴムを丸かじりしてるような食感……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "ご、豪快にいったわね……！\nそれで、味の方はどうかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "す、凄い……！　グミの中に沢山小さいグミが\n入ってて、グミのマトリョーシカみたい！　感動だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "でしょう！　いろんな味と食感を楽しんでもらいたくて\nグミ生地で小粒のグミを包んだグミケーキにしたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "沢山の味と噛み応えが次々襲い掛かってきて……\nこんなの味覚のラビリンスだよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんも一緒に食べよ？\nほら、反対側からかぶりついて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.5000091553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "じゃ、じゃあ私も遠慮なくいただきま……待って\n事務所の真ん中で二人して巨大グミにかじりつく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "冷静に考えてみると、これ、ちゃんとお祝いに\nなってるのか不安になってきたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.1333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "特大バースデーグミでお祝いしてもらったの人生初だよ\nありがとうね、瑠依ちゃん！　すっごく楽しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.5999959309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_53_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "た、楽しい？　美味しいじゃなくて……？\nまあ、さくらが喜んでるなら良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.2666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}